Dar es Salaam &mdash; Prime Minister Kassim Majaliwa has suspended Energy and Water Utility Regulatory Authority (EWURA) Director General Mr Felix Ngamlagosi.A two paragraph statement, which was released by the Director of Presidential Communication Mr Gerson Msigwa, indicates that the suspension is effective from June 11.However, the statement, which was released on Sunday at around 1am didn't explain the reasons behind Mr Ngamlagosi's suspension.